<Content>Great Stay I took my family during the Christmas vacation. We had two of the newly remodeled rooms with a beautiful views of the mountains.The reort has something for everyone. My wife and I played golf on their golf course, didn't play well but we had a lot of fun.My granddaughter and kids spent a lot of time at the water park or one of the many pools. The weather was a little cool but all the pools are heated.We ate at two of the restaurants on the resort property and found them to be a good value.The resort is close to some great shopping.All and all we had a great time. 
